    "en": "He said: A band of Jews had accepted Islam, among them Abdullah ibn Salam, Asad, Tha'laba, Ibn Yamin, and Ibn Suraya. They came to the Prophet (may God bless him and his family) and said: \"O Prophet of God! Indeed, Musa (peace be upon him) appointed Yusha' ibn Nun. So who is your successor, O Messenger of God, and who is our guardian after you?\"",
